- What can he say?

420
00:36:21,770 --> 00:36:24,534
My son's a crow that flew away
with a pearl...? Huh?

421
00:36:25,007 --> 00:36:26,736
Adi's a monkey who dropped out?

422
00:36:27,643 --> 00:36:31,977
That's nothing, Sumi! Natu-bhai is
now this monkey's father-in-law!

423
00:36:33,983 --> 00:36:38,750
Your daughter Pooja ran away to
marry my son Adi!

424
00:36:39,321 --> 00:36:41,221
lshu... please!
- Right!

425
00:36:42,291 --> 00:36:45,886
Natu-bhai, we're now relatives.
Please say peace

426
00:36:46,095 --> 00:36:48,063
Could you folks embrace...?

427
00:36:49,031 --> 00:36:52,057
Well, if not embrace, you can
atleast sweeten your tongues...?

428
00:36:52,534 --> 00:36:56,834
