l went home, Adi told me
that you were here. so...

524
00:46:16,565 --> 00:46:18,533
What did they have to say?

525
00:46:22,938 --> 00:46:24,838
Sumi...
- l don't want to hear it

526
00:46:25,974 --> 00:46:28,534
Sumi, the reports...
- No! l don't believe it!

527
00:46:30,679 --> 00:46:32,544
You mustn't believe it either!

528
00:46:33,582 --> 00:46:36,779
