- What...?!

750
01:07:40,647 --> 01:07:42,979
Sumi, Pooja dear, l,
lshwarchand Thakur...

751
01:07:43,584 --> 01:07:48,715
give my son 10 years of freedom
to make his dreams come true

752
01:07:49,089 --> 01:07:53,082
