- That's what l'm asking...

866
01:17:53,092 --> 01:17:55,390
why has the fan stopped?
- Whom are you asking?

867
01:17:56,929 --> 01:18:00,888
l'm asking you, Laxman ! You !
- l see.. it's me. But what?

868
01:18:07,140 --> 01:18:09,700
Why has the fan stopped working?

869
01:18:09,909 --> 01:18:12,400
