Hi, dad... c'mon !
''We're emperors...''

873
01:18:24,691 --> 01:18:26,591
Didn't l tell you dad would come?
- Laxman...

874
01:18:27,627 --> 01:18:30,425
have you brought the broom?
- This one...?

875
01:18:31,130 --> 01:18:36,432
Yes, Laxman. Give that broom to me.
Now, this moment... in these hands

876
01:18:39,005 --> 01:18:40,905
And go on now.
- Where to?

877
01:18:41,140 --> 01:18:44,439
Take this fuse. And hide it
someplace no one can find it

878
01:18:44,711 --> 01:18:46,679
Go on.
- May l hide it behind the fridge?

879
01:18:47,013 --> 01:18:50,449
Give that to me. Take your stuff,
switch on the AC in Adi's room...

880
01:18:50,583 --> 01:18:52,551
and go to sleep. Hurry!
- Now...?

881
01:18:54,087 --> 01:18:56,055
You aren't doing this to
irritate me, are you?

882
01:18:56,689 --> 01:18:58,919
You're the one who's doing things
to irritate us dad, not him

883
